./my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:37:**Phase 2 — Core rule stack (CCH-011..CCH-021).** R1 Metric Accent, R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH parabolic), R3 Agogic Accent, R4 Duration Contrast, R5 Final Ritardando (Friberg–Sundberg square-root), R6 Punctuation+Breath, R7 Articulation Shaping, R8 Microtiming Polish (below JND). Role-filter gating so grid-locked voices skip the stack. Phrase-feature extraction via partitura. End-of-phase: single-voice melodic passages sound shaped, not flat; metric gate shows structured deviations vs. flat-line baseline.
